      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOLD THRUSTER (8) settled well back early on debut and but the line nicely when second (25.84) at Geelong over 460m. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. BIOLLANTE (6) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last time finished 3rd on July 13 over 515m at this track behind Breach beaten 11 lengths (30.69) in a Restricted WIN. Hard to beat again. ASTON LOUISE (3) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a 1.3 lengths second (30.64) in a Maiden at The Meadows. Can find the frame this time. FLOREAT PICA (1) is new to this track but not to be underestimated.",
